# cordova-plugin-pdfviewer

A Cordova plugin to open PDF files **within** your mobile app (supports Android & iOS).  
Built for Ionic 7 + Angular apps.

## Features
- Open PDFs inside the app (not via browser)
- Zoom In / Out
- Page navigation (Next, Prev, First, Last)
- Touch gestures (planned)

## Installation
```bash
cordova plugin add https://github.com/theDynamicAIArtist/cordova-plugin-pdfviewer.git
